    @{b}Pict2Source@{ub} is a Public Domain FreeWare Program. You can spread this
    version everywhere but you can't modify the files in the package and the
    package itself.

    @{fg fill} NOTE: @{fg text}
    @{b}Pict2Source@{ub} is a program that uses datatypes availables from version
    3.0 of the O.S. so it is necessary that tou have it on your Workbench.It is also
    necessary in your FONT: drawer the @{b}newtopaz.font@{ub} font that you can
    find in this package. Also this Hypertext uses some features of AmigaGuide
    availables from O.S. 3.0 only.

                @{" What is Pict2Source            "link what}

                @{" How Pict2Source was born       "link why}

                @{" How to use Pict2Source         "link start}

